Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.23,0:00:05.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.84,0:00:11.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.72,0:00:27.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.19,0:00:33.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.93,0:00:42.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.37,0:00:48.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.08,0:00:55.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.45,0:01:00.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.92,0:01:03.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.29,0:01:15.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.41,0:01:24.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦妳了立花中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.95,0:02:01.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠著妳收集的資料\N地球應該能更確實的邁向勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.65,0:02:05.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下我們的計劃\N也能更順利的發展下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.36,0:02:13.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張金卡代表著\N我們對妳的感謝之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:28.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「嘆息的玫瑰唸珠」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然身體上沒有任何異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.92,0:03:51.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因為精神上極度疲勞\N還是請各位晚一點再會面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問妳喔蒂卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.13,0:03:55.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓莉露小姐獨處不會有問題吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不用擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她馬上就會恢復吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露窺視到了外星異種的"記憶"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那些情報量太大\N所以才會產生精神錯亂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文是這麼告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種(傑拉拜亞)的記憶是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:26.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是雷文還是桑德曼\N一定還有些什麼重要的事瞞著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們找各位找了好久\N少爺、小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.67,0:04:35.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐她不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.34,0:04:43.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天一大早就沒看到她\N結果到她房間一看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桌上只留下了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.02,0:04:52.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我突然不告而別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.96,0:04:57.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來隸屬的單位\N正是EFA的情報部...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說吧\N我就是EFA派來的間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:06.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了盜取超重神的機密資料\N才隱瞞身份潛入城內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要EFA戰力能增強的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.64,0:05:12.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和外星異種的戰爭\N也就能結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然相處時間很短\N不論如何我都很感謝各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了...\N和你們在一起我很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.58,0:05:23.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定有什麼地方搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼他們有下達什麼指示嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N他們說沒有必要去追她回來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該早就通通知道了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是莉露的事...\N就連綾香的事也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼重要的事都瞞著我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暗中拿我們逗樂子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.37,0:05:42.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生才不會是那樣子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.08,0:05:49.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我真是太不知分寸了\N我...我怎麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都明白的蝶雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.58,0:05:58.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐總是那麼堅強\N也是我們大家所憧憬的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.56,0:06:03.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(北之塔的密碼...幫我問候綾香喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湛藍的海恬靜的海濱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的...好安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來媚月真的是間諜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...到現在還沒辦法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和超重皇的停機坪好像哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道這是什麼玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這種東西\N只要隨便摸它個兩下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在玩什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會是什麼難道你...哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是立體虛擬影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.91,0:08:03.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會有身在水中的感覺\N但還是能呼吸和說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為這下死定了呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好險...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是哪裡的海中映像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡的...會是哪兒呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼了?發生什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城市被...太悽慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡...難道是...地球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是...並不是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(本日破曉前)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(傑拉拜亞大量殺戮機系統)\N(自衛星軌道上...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在說什麼啊?\N(展開了無差別攻擊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(使得機械城市遭到了致命性損害)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好悽慘...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...海洋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.44,0:09:02.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭比亞斯的海洋汙染\N已經到達極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不撤離的話\N我們就只有全滅一途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭比亞斯的那些傢伙\N還想要來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.29,0:09:21.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們瑟力亞斯光是為了維持現狀\N就已經精疲力竭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法再接受更多移民了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.89,0:09:29.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們老早就逃到開拓星球\N居然還有臉對留守者見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.37,0:09:33.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們故意這麼晚來\N是想奪走我們辛苦建設的成果嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位請稍安勿躁\N先看看這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是桑德曼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用我們正在開發中的創星機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用超重Σ的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說是瑟力亞斯星的開發\N就連蘭比亞斯的污染也能夠終止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:58.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紙上談兵的空談就免了吧疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是連找個駕駛員都有問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.50,0:10:07.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑拉拜亞博士\N您的大舅子好像還沒認清事實嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.47,0:10:10.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這表示桑德曼和外星異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是從外星來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來傑拉拜亞(外星異種)\N是取自別人的名字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.48,0:10:18.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然桑德曼是傑拉拜亞的大舅子\N這麼說來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是莉露.傑拉拜亞的\N親戚之類的囉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼! 桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露她...是我的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.84,0:10:48.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭似乎...已經無法避免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到我們的創星機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.51,0:10:56.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到超重Σ...\N連星球都能創造的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的想法應該就會改變才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說對吧雷文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的星球正要滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.86,0:11:11.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了活下去只有進行屠殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.27,0:11:14.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那也算是正義的話那我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以完全自主行動的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制會對目標地點趕盡殺絕\N的"大量殺戮機系統"...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您真的認為有必要用這種機械嗎?\N修紀大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.38,0:11:30.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣蘭比亞斯數十億的生命\N將能因此得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為會自然分解\N所以也不會造成污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.62,0:11:37.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為此而犧牲瑟力亞斯數萬條生命\N我實在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果非得要流血的話\N還是流的越少越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.73,0:11:44.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼覺得嗎?疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.57,0:11:49.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不弄髒自己的手\N連打倒的對手有多痛都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣根本是機械才有的行為模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是人類該用的手段!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.31,0:11:59.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在機械外殼下又何妨\N我們非得要繼續活下去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箭也已經射出去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算硬碰硬我也要阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.85,0:12:09.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連一個人都救不了的你\N又還能做些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.06,0:12:16.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我妹妹...\N害露菲拉早死的人就是你疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果光會空談理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.37,0:12:22.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法營造等質結果的話\N那就一點意義也沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重Σ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創星機?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把控制裝置給...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.14,0:12:58.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道...\N自己現在到底做了些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:04.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不受控制的大量殺戮機系統\N將會開始失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說是瑟力亞斯了\N就連蘭比亞斯上的一切生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會被趕盡殺絕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量殺戮機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠超重神的原型機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.55,0:15:19.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人...人被壓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.89,0:15:28.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.29,0:15:34.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉原諒我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不應該...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不應該是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.07,0:15:39.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才和我分開妻子就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.44,0:16:20.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨著我的修紀.傑拉拜亞\N也死在瓦礫堆下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑟力亞斯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.11,0:16:24.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭比亞斯的所有同胞們\N也全都死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.91,0:16:28.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我獨自在這\N遙遠的星球上苟活著...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了時空?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.06,0:16:39.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據逃生艇航道\N進行自動追溯的結果判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是中途\N空間跳躍失敗的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.03,0:16:46.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對她的主觀時間來說\N就只是經過了數個月而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.68,0:17:02.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到這個新天地\N我的同胞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能活著真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.53,0:17:14.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人...就是莉露嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.33,0:17:19.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露.傑拉拜亞\N這是連她自己都忘掉的本名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.14,0:17:24.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會失去記憶也是能理解的\N像這種痛苦的記憶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露她...她知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.81,0:17:31.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不修紀.傑拉拜亞並沒有\N告訴她我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.01,0:17:35.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他沒讓我知道\N莉露出生的事情一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她平靜下來之後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算以父親的身份和她相認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.56,0:17:44.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來莉露並不是孤獨一個人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.19,0:17:47.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望她的精神能快點恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和外星異種的接觸\N造成了她的記憶陸續恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還處於精神不穩定的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想請諸位\N暫時先在一旁靜靜看護就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這包在我們身上吧對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今沒告訴諸位一切真相\N都怪我太懦弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.01,0:18:08.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今之後還希望諸位能和我\N一同繼續奮戰下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.25,0:18:11.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是我一廂情願的請求\N但拜託諸位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.39,0:18:14.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生才不會是那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.36,0:18:19.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你主動拜託別人...\N感覺起來還真不像你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會讓這顆星球\N也變成那樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連星球也能創造的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創星機是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很寂寞吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.17,0:19:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起打擾到你了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以到外面來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.38,0:19:11.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為睡在房裡的話\N就會一直做惡夢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我也想快點好起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.02,0:19:22.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得心裡好煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.69,0:19:25.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是要想起什麼似的\N卻又想不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.26,0:19:32.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔心著我到底遺忘了什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.21,0:19:39.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙這裡到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心吧莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看過這個\N妳就能明白一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼他就是你的爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅...修紀舅舅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有個會去迎接妳的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼自己也都不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.03,0:20:33.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼啊...\N莉露他就是你的爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂到底又怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想要讓她高興...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...你讓她看了那些東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(希望妳能把我當做妳的親人)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅你在哪裡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那傢伙沒來的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別碰她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.74,0:21:18.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.48,0:21:25.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脈搏減弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救護班快一點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.62,0:21:28.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.42,0:21:34.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道就不會\N體諒一下別人的心情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.86,0:21:37.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓莉露看到那些畫面\N她會怎麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不會多考慮一下嗎?\N你這個機械混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.78,0:22:03.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.39,0:22:11.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.49,0:22:20.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.24,0:22:28.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.28,0:22:37.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.45,0:22:44.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.03,0:22:46.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.56,0:22:53.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.70,0:22:56.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.47,0:23:03.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.65,0:23:10.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.75,0:23:13.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.82,0:23:21.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.54,0:23:29.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神的秘密終於揭開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.84,0:23:33.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這只是一場重大悲劇\N的序幕而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.21,0:23:35.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺\N請您打起精神來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.58,0:23:39.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家...愛娜不論發生什麼事\N都會一直陪伴在您身旁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.58,0:23:42.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入沈睡中的莉露\N掉進悲慟之中的桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.38,0:23:43.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.39,0:23:46.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警終於揭開面紗\N展露出駭人威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.02,0:23:49.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回「粉碎的女神(機組)」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.09,0:23:52.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會守護住斗牙少爺的!


